data.description: Stunning home in highly desired Redbridge subdivision in Redwater school district.  This beauty boasts gorgeous 18 ft. ceilings in the main living area that is an open concept to kitchen and dining.  Kitchen has subway tile, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances.  All bathrooms and laundry room have granite countertops, as well.  Gorgeous hand-scraped hardwood floors throughout main living areas, ceramic tile in all bathrooms and laundry room, and carpet in the bedrooms. Back porch overlooks wooded acreage, has a gas stub for grill, and a custom built TV niche with cable hookups for entertainment.  The office is a quiet safe haven that you'll love to work in, or it can easily be converted into a formal dining room if preferred.  Master bedroom has double boxed ceiling, walk-in his and her closets, and master bath en-suite with his/her vanities, large glass enclosed shower and jetted tub. The family will love the large bonus/game room upstairs that can be used for entertainment and/or movie room. Custom items in house:  built-in locker for kids' drop-off area; safe room/hideaway; built-in dressers in master closet with peg board for jewelry; one bedroom has built-in window seat with bookshelves; built-in ironing board in laundry room; built-in hunting storage in garage; wine fridge in kitchen; crown molding.  THIS HOUSE IS A MUST SEE - PICTURES DON'T DO IT JUSTICE!!
